{
  "analysis": "The jq command is not available, and the custody_manifest.json file doesn't exist yet. I need to manually sort the JSON manifest using standard tools and ensure the archive is properly created.",
  "plan": "I will manually implement the JSON sorting logic using awk and sort. I'll reconstruct the manifest file, sort the entries by filepath, and write the final compact JSON manifest. Then I'll verify both deliverables.",
  "commands": [
    {
